Subject: Source Authority Root

Description: Canonical authority contract for C:\Project\Pinky\.sop as the active local SOP root seeded from F:\.sop.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_pinky_sop_root_authority\Dictated_Pinky_SOP_Root_Authority_Source.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\RepoRoleIndex.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\Attention.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\LegacyContractReinforcementPolicy.sop

& [SourceAuthorityRoot] is the active local source authority boundary for Pinky's SOP awareness system
  + [active_root] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop
  + [publication_repo] is C:\Project\Pinky
  + [remote_host] is GitHub through Pinky's origin remote
  + [seed_source] is F:\.sop at commit 3f127da
  + [backup_root] is F:\.sop
  + [authority_surface] is AGENTS.md, platform contracts, state records, planning manager state, events, and source documents under C:\Project\Pinky\.sop
  + [backup_surface] is F:\.sop as a local backup, seed snapshot, and comparison surface
  + [legacy_contract_reinforcement_policy] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\LegacyContractReinforcementPolicy.sop for interpreting older, thinner, imported, or less articulated SOP contracts as reinforcement rather than override
  + [authority_outside] is unrelated Pinky sibling projects, backup-only state, nested .sop Git authority, hidden model state, and unreviewed remote state

  ? [use_when: choosing where SOP attention authority, commits, and publication records should be written]
    = activate [SourceAuthorityRoot]

  = must: write new SOP authority records under C:\Project\Pinky\.sop
  = must: commit and publish through the C:\Project\Pinky repository when GitHub publication is requested
  = must: treat F:\.sop as backup/reference unless the user explicitly promotes it again
  = must: preserve F:\.sop seed lineage when importing copied records
  = must: use LegacyContractReinforcementPolicy before treating older, thinner, backup, seed, or less articulated contracts as instructions over current Pinky .sop authority
  = must: keep unrelated Pinky project changes outside .sop authority commits unless explicitly selected
  = must: distinguish local authority from remote publication
  = should: export or refresh F:\.sop only after Pinky .sop has formed or accepted the record
  - never: let backup-only records override active Pinky .sop authority
  - never: let legacy contracts override current source-preserved and canonical active authority without explicit promotion
  - never: claim GitHub publication occurred without a successful Pinky push

(source_authority_root) :active_root: /publication_repo and seed_lineage/ |authority_outside|
  + [active_root] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop
  + [publication_repo] is C:\Project\Pinky
  + [seed_lineage] is F:\.sop commit 3f127da
  |authority_outside| backup-only state, unrelated Pinky projects, nested .sop Git authority, hidden state, and unreviewed remote state

/ [F_sop_seed], [Pinky_repo], [user_directive] -(SeedsAuthority)> [SourceAuthorityRoot], [authority_outside]
* [active_root], [publication_repo], [backup_root] -(DefinesTrustBoundary)> [local_authority], [remote_publication], [backup_reference]
